    "There are few PTCHS dataset available, lacking adequate hazard categories and highquality mask annotations in complex transmission corridor scenarios.",
    "2) Segmentation quality.",
    "Even after dedicated fine-tuning on PTCHS data, SAM struggles to deal with target objects with fine structure in complex background.",
    "For instance, as shown in the second and fourth columns of Fig. 1, the segmentation on tower crane from SAM is severely interfered by surrounding buildings or equipment.",
    "To solve the above challenges, we start by constructing the first large-scale benchmark for PTCHS, ELE-40K, containing 44,094 pixel-level annotated image-mask pairs derived from real-world transmission corridors."
